description: Water views from all rooms...This one-bedroom condo is well-located across from the SB Yacht Club and the causeway to the Sugar Bowl and tastefully renovated in 2018, including custom moldings & trims, refinished hardwood floors, and an SS/Marble kitchen with custom white cabinets. The basement is highlighted by the shared laundry room and deeded storage units for each unit that you'll be hard-pressed to fill. The HOA fee includes both heat and hot water. Lennon Court residents enjoy a shared courtyard and first-come, first-served parking for ten cars.
